    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "SAN FRANCISCO /\nOAKLAND\nEFFECTIVE JUNE 1, 1964\nUNITED\nUNITED JETS\nTO HAWAII . . .\nECONOMY COACH JETS\nONLY $100\nCUSTOM COACH JETS\nONLY $110*\n(see map page)",
      "ELKO\nGRAND JUNCTION\nDENVER\nMONTERE\nSALINAS\nVISALIA\nUNITED FLIES BY ELGIN WATCH TIME\nTRANSCONTINENTAL NONSTOP JET SERVICE\nESTON\nPROVIDENCE\nNEVERK\nNEWART\nMOLINE-ROCK\nAND-DAVENPORT\nLINGULN\nSAMSUURE\nNORFOLK PORTSMOUTH\nINGSPURT-JOHNSUN GI\nGREENSBORO\nRALEIGH - DURHAM\nWEST PALM BEACH\nREALERSAR\nUNITED INCREASES JET SCHEDULES\nTO HAWAII • • • 23 JETS A WEEK+\nUnited offers you a wide choice of service and\nschedules to Hawaii ... a total of 23 flights\nweekly to Hawaii. Here are some of the features\nof Custom Coach service: Your choice of cock-\ntails or champagne for your aloha toast!. A\ndelicious full-course meal specially prepared in\nour world-famous flight kitchens!. A Hawaiian\nsteward and\ncolorfully attired stewardesses to\nprovide excellent in-flight service! All this for $23\nless than ever before.\n*Effective June 1 Subject to Government Approval\n†Schedules Effective June 5\nUNITED\nTHE EXTRA CARE AIRLINE"
    ],
